items.title: Chartist Talks: Sudeep Shah of SBI Securities explains why he is bullish on Havells, Indian Hotels
items.description: The stock of Mahindra and Mahindra has given a downward sloping trendline breakout on a daily scale. This breakout is confirmed by robust volume.

items.title: Momentum could push Nifty 50 towards 26,000, pick these 3 stocks for better return, says Anand Rathi's Jigar Patel
items.description: With the fresh breakout, the current momentum could push the Nifty 50 toward 26,000 or higher. Despite this, Patel remains cautious on the long side, as several warning signs have emerged.
